{"tid":305544,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"朋友隻狗走失佐 幫幫手！","createTime":"2017-07-01T17:50:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-02T23:07:02.000Z","uid":8215,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9f68eeb48861168e26ea19f701c7eab30c3859ad","tid":305544,"uid":8215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T17:50:39.000Z","msg":"事緣<br />\n朋友屋企係有圍牆 圍住幾棟村屋<br />\n佢媽媽每朝洗衫都會放佢2隻狗出去圍牆內既空地跑 因為洗衣機都係屋外<br />\n咁圍牆有幾個電閘 係比車出入個啲<br />\n鄰居出完車無閂好 咁岩佢媽無留意到<br />\n發現既時已經走佐出去<br />\n朝早7點幾唔見 搵佐好耐都搵唔到<br />\n以前試過一次 有自己返黎<br />\n但今次等到而家都無返<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/02/014905_4a8387ef1d88f110a5c56ba06819fafa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F02%2F014905_4a8387ef1d88f110a5c56ba06819fafa.jpg&h=8bfd9480&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/02/014906_204cd635367932e273b1897a58e603e9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F02%2F014906_204cd635367932e273b1897a58e603e9.jpg&h=b175754f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果住附近既麻煩留意下 唔該哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n八鄉錦田嗰邊 但比較近八鄉"},{"pid":"736301948cf5715ab793b715802d8c64f054064d","tid":305544,"uid":32298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T17:52:02.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd01597df770c010659339e60430dd5a2e85eaa1","tid":305544,"uid":8215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T17:53:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔該哂巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  幫下手比正評睇下推唔推到上熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  因為成10歲 所以好擔心"},{"pid":"6b4b8afda71251c41a9ff690a6944e2b8a7eece8","tid":305544,"uid":58550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T17:54:10.000Z","msg":"Pushhhh<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"586c55c6c4cdc6a2743d85637d90a4b73cd06d7f","tid":305544,"uid":8215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T17:54:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/02/015417_2f99a9397c3290a267b7db35f94fabc7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F02%2F015417_2f99a9397c3290a267b7db35f94fabc7.jpg&h=89bf569d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有張正面圖 唔該各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f41717830d8e28ac7da4c434e20fd9ae5ebf7b70","tid":305544,"uid":25106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T17:55:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望搵到"},{"pid":"79a4374abe82317f499d9a0b1a0b21489a1b197e","tid":305544,"uid":61050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T17:55:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6031cbd0eb148fac9117c697f2ac8b424bcaf929","tid":305544,"uid":7998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T17:55:57.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dac9500fe446833c9c45fc73012347e8e8b49558","tid":305544,"uid":8215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T17:55:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Pushhhh<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n成10歲真係好擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都知朋友媽咪無留意到 疏忽佐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7b804f1f25e5ea3d204bbdd6e8f852afb856c13","tid":305544,"uid":8215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T17:56:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望搵到</blockquote><br />\n我朋友搵佐全日 之後要返工 都特登搵其他朋友去佢到試下等 但仲未等到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2993a7916ce6a34888e401ebdfd317e096234b13","tid":305544,"uid":32298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T18:02:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔該哂巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  幫下手比正評睇下推唔推到上熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  因為成10歲 所以好擔心</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n不過好似聽講話d狗如果覺得生命到盡頭，會靜靜雞搵個地方匿埋死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw希望樓主你搵得番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26ebcf45d8311c8431249e15dd98d84b93322162","tid":305544,"uid":8215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T18:03:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔該哂巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  幫下手比正評睇下推唔推到上熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  因為成10歲 所以好擔心</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n不過好似聽講話d狗如果覺得生命到盡頭，會靜靜雞搵個地方匿埋死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw希望樓主你搵得番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n 唔好嚇我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  由細睇住佢大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d52ef887fcb65e5b8c686e49b7be348f1dbd3559","tid":305544,"uid":549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T18:09:24.000Z","msg":"有養狗既幫你推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b305fabef32b8a31aec123a1249d7f31b5d46bd3","tid":305544,"uid":12823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T18:12:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c71db2ec20576cb890366e6491d106493170283e","tid":305544,"uid":7049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T18:13:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f951907b6f998217e763c54a0a11e33f1f47aa0b","tid":305544,"uid":7049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T18:13:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e577c9233d8315c8a9330f87aa3d4eb9048edaf6","tid":305544,"uid":7049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T18:13:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4b3eb246baf99a5f881f392857440fa458dff546","tid":305544,"uid":8215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T18:14:42.000Z","msg":"唔該哂各位巴絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有咩消息會更新 希望搵得返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a02cc74f1b8c0288361d07cca2085f53d292c69","tid":305544,"uid":16283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T18:18:50.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5847a08c2a19649f34ed1740852ee73e90bb14bc","tid":305544,"uid":7923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl